1
00:02:02,120 --> 00:02:03,319
Um

2
00:02:05,160 --> 00:02:06,000
You go first.

3
00:02:06,360 --> 00:02:07,400
Or should you go first?

4
00:02:07,480 --> 00:02:08,240
Today

5
00:02:08,399 --> 00:02:09,479
is the happiest day

6
00:02:09,600 --> 00:02:10,839
of my entire life.

7
00:02:11,960 --> 00:02:12,919
Me too.

8
00:02:13,679 --> 00:02:14,320
Sir

9
00:02:14,399 --> 00:02:16,000
Buy a sky lantern for your lady.

10
00:02:16,080 --> 00:02:17,600
Today is the Sky Lantern Festival.

11
00:02:17,839 --> 00:02:19,279
Lovers release sky lanterns together

12
00:02:19,320 --> 00:02:20,720
to ensure everlasting happiness.

13
00:02:27,639 --> 00:02:29,119
I got it wrong again.

14
00:02:29,600 --> 00:02:32,080
Today is my first time selling sky lanterns.

15
00:02:32,360 --> 00:02:34,759
I’ve asked several people and got it wrong each time.

16
00:02:35,039 --> 00:02:37,440
Looks like I won’t be able to sell this lantern.

17
00:02:38,520 --> 00:02:39,479
Little one

18
00:02:40,119 --> 00:02:41,360
I’ll take all these lanterns.

19
00:02:41,600 --> 00:02:42,600
She and I

20
00:02:43,759 --> 00:02:44,800
She and I

21
00:02:45,119 --> 00:02:46,039
will definitely

22
00:02:46,520 --> 00:02:48,000
be happy for a lifetime.

23
00:02:50,639 --> 00:02:51,520
Here, for you.

24
00:02:52,720 --> 00:02:53,520
Thank you.

25
00:02:53,600 --> 00:02:55,440
Wishing you and your lady everlasting love.

26
00:02:55,479 --> 00:02:56,639
And may you have children soon.

27
00:02:59,479 --> 00:03:00,919
Who’s your lady?

28
00:03:03,479 --> 00:03:04,639
Just now,

29
00:03:04,800 --> 00:03:06,919
it was just a kid, so I...

30
00:03:08,399 --> 00:03:09,240
I know.

31
00:03:09,320 --> 00:03:11,039
You were just worried she wouldn’t sell all her lanterns

32
00:03:11,119 --> 00:03:12,399
and would be punished when she got home.

33
00:03:12,639 --> 00:03:14,759
That’s why you helped her.

34
00:03:15,279 --> 00:03:17,399
So we don’t need to release the lanterns now, right?

35
00:03:17,600 --> 00:03:18,600
No, no, we have to.

36
00:03:18,639 --> 00:03:19,520
We must release them.

37
00:03:20,320 --> 00:03:21,440
Didn’t you say

38
00:03:21,800 --> 00:03:22,919
if you spend money

39
00:03:23,399 --> 00:03:24,880
and don’t use it, it’s a waste?

40
00:03:24,919 --> 00:03:25,919
Shameful.

41
00:03:31,360 --> 00:03:32,759
It's a pity

42
00:03:33,119 --> 00:03:34,800
that only here has the Sky Lantern Festival.

43
00:03:35,559 --> 00:03:36,800
I don't know when

44
00:03:36,839 --> 00:03:39,039
I'll be able to see such a beautiful sight again.

45
00:03:39,600 --> 00:03:41,720
Although only here has the Sky Lantern Festival,

46
00:03:41,759 --> 00:03:42,839
other places

47
00:03:43,080 --> 00:03:44,399
have the Shangyuan Lantern Festival.

48
00:03:44,639 --> 00:03:45,520
I promise you,

49
00:03:45,720 --> 00:03:47,039
no matter where we go in the future,

50
00:03:47,119 --> 00:03:48,199
I'll always go with you.

51
00:03:48,320 --> 00:03:49,399
To the Shangyuan Lantern Festival.

52
00:03:49,479 --> 00:03:50,520
Then you can't go back on your word.

53
00:03:50,600 --> 00:03:51,639
Why would I go back on my word?

54
00:03:51,759 --> 00:03:53,199
It's my honor.

55
00:03:53,759 --> 00:03:54,960
Come on, let's go release the lanterns.

56
00:03:55,039 --> 00:03:55,839
Let's go.

57
00:04:02,160 --> 00:04:03,639
I bet those two

58
00:04:03,880 --> 00:04:06,000
are probably releasing sky lanterns right now.

59
00:04:06,759 --> 00:04:08,360
I heard from the people in town

60
00:04:08,559 --> 00:04:10,119
that during their Sky Lantern Festival

61
00:04:10,160 --> 00:04:12,000
if lovers release sky lanterns together,

62
00:04:12,039 --> 00:04:13,399
they'll be happy together forever.

63
00:04:15,759 --> 00:04:17,519
That's really enviable.

64
00:04:19,600 --> 00:04:20,559
Yeah.

65
00:04:21,440 --> 00:04:22,640
It really is enviable.

66
00:04:26,000 --> 00:04:27,239
Even you, with your icy face,

67
00:04:27,239 --> 00:04:28,839
feel envy sometimes.

68
00:04:30,720 --> 00:04:32,160
We're both unlucky people,

69
00:04:32,320 --> 00:04:33,720
do we really need to hurt each other?

70
00:04:35,359 --> 00:04:36,320
True.

71
00:04:41,040 --> 00:04:43,079
What if a sky lantern actually falls down on us,

72
00:04:43,160 --> 00:04:44,200
what should we do?

73
00:04:44,320 --> 00:04:45,119
What else can we do?

74
00:04:45,200 --> 00:04:46,160
I'll block it for you.

75
00:04:48,119 --> 00:04:50,559
You may look cold as ice,

76
00:04:50,600 --> 00:04:52,399
but you're surprisingly warm-hearted.

77
00:04:54,640 --> 00:04:55,480
Thanks.

78
00:04:57,880 --> 00:04:58,920
Two taels of silver.

79
00:05:00,160 --> 00:05:02,160
I was just making an example, and you want two taels of silver?

80
00:05:02,200 --> 00:05:03,440
You're way too mercenary.

81
00:05:03,799 --> 00:05:05,519
I wasted my sympathy on you just now.

82
00:05:05,760 --> 00:05:06,399
Fine.

83
00:05:06,640 --> 00:05:07,559
Half price, then.

84
00:05:08,839 --> 00:05:09,799
So our friendship

85
00:05:09,799 --> 00:05:10,839
is only worth one tael of silver?

86
00:05:10,880 --> 00:05:12,519
You, the assistant apprentice of Dianchasi,

87
00:05:12,839 --> 00:05:15,160
were threatening to beat and kill us just a few days ago.

88
00:05:15,359 --> 00:05:16,720
Is there even any friendship between us?

89
00:05:18,679 --> 00:05:19,600
Good point.

90
00:05:27,760 --> 00:05:28,559
Cheers.

91
00:05:28,799 --> 00:05:30,200
To two disappointed people.

92
00:05:46,000 --> 00:05:46,959
It's getting late.

93
00:05:47,000 --> 00:05:48,160
You should head back soon.

94
00:06:03,399 --> 00:06:04,000
Sir,

95
00:06:04,040 --> 00:06:05,079
are you going out?

96
00:06:05,200 --> 00:06:05,799
Yes.

97
00:06:07,799 --> 00:06:08,519
Sir

98
00:06:09,079 --> 00:06:10,880
Where are you going so late?

99
00:06:11,040 --> 00:06:12,239
I have important business to attend to.

100
00:06:13,880 --> 00:06:14,720
Sir

101
00:06:15,359 --> 00:06:16,559
Are you angry?

102
00:06:17,359 --> 00:06:18,320
Are you jealous?

103
00:06:19,040 --> 00:06:19,959
Who’s jealous?

104
00:06:20,799 --> 00:06:22,799
What important business could there be this late?

105
00:06:23,119 --> 00:06:24,480
My thoughts these past few days

106
00:06:24,519 --> 00:06:25,839
surely haven’t escaped your notice.

107
00:06:25,839 --> 00:06:27,119
I might as well be direct.

108
00:06:28,799 --> 00:06:30,920
I’ve admired you for a long time.

109
00:06:31,119 --> 00:06:33,000
Ever since I joined the Diancha Office,

110
00:06:33,119 --> 00:06:33,679
In the past,

111
00:06:33,760 --> 00:06:35,200
I know you were young and playful.

112
00:06:35,320 --> 00:06:37,119
But now we work together at the Diancha Office.

113
00:06:37,399 --> 00:06:38,279
Jokes like this

114
00:06:38,480 --> 00:06:39,760
shouldn’t be made anymore.

115
00:06:40,160 --> 00:06:41,559
How could this be a joke?

116
00:06:41,600 --> 00:06:43,279
Every word comes from the bottom of my heart.

117
00:06:43,320 --> 00:06:44,600
You sure have a lot of “bottom of your heart.”

118
00:06:44,640 --> 00:06:46,000
You said you love makeup and powder,

119
00:06:46,160 --> 00:06:47,160
and that’s from the bottom of your heart.

120
00:06:47,440 --> 00:06:48,720
You love delicacies,

121
00:06:48,839 --> 00:06:50,040
also from the bottom of your heart.

122
00:06:50,359 --> 00:06:51,640
People eat all kinds of grains,

123
00:06:51,880 --> 00:06:52,839
but in your heart,

124
00:06:53,040 --> 00:06:54,239
how can you fit so much?

125
00:06:54,440 --> 00:06:55,040
But

126
00:06:55,119 --> 00:06:57,119
I really do have orders to return to the capital tonight.

127
00:06:58,040 --> 00:06:59,320
You don’t need to come with me.

128
00:06:59,399 --> 00:07:00,839
Stay with Lu Jiu for now.

129
00:07:00,920 --> 00:07:02,679
First, to continue investigating the Wuxiang treasure.

130
00:07:03,000 --> 00:07:04,000
Second, to assist them

131
00:07:04,119 --> 00:07:05,000
in going deep into Gushan

132
00:07:05,119 --> 00:07:06,160
to eliminate the human traffickers.

133
00:07:07,480 --> 00:07:08,200
Sir

134
00:07:08,320 --> 00:07:09,160
Sir

135
00:07:35,480 --> 00:07:36,480
What?

136
00:07:36,959 --> 00:07:39,399
They didn't stay in Mist Town to look for clues.

137
00:07:39,480 --> 00:07:40,799
Instead, they went straight to Lone Mountain.

138
00:07:40,839 --> 00:07:42,519
Lone Mountain is just a rabble.

139
00:07:42,559 --> 00:07:44,119
If Tianluo sends a team,

140
00:07:44,160 --> 00:07:45,959
they could wipe it out in no time.

141
00:07:47,480 --> 00:07:50,239
Lone Mountain isn't something just anyone can mess with.

142
00:08:06,320 --> 00:08:07,440
Come on, you two.

143
00:08:07,600 --> 00:08:08,760
Just be straightforward.

144
00:08:08,839 --> 00:08:10,119
All this flirting with your eyes,

145
00:08:10,320 --> 00:08:11,640
do you think others can't see it?

146
00:08:12,320 --> 00:08:13,519
What nonsense are you talking about?

147
00:08:13,600 --> 00:08:15,119
Who's flirting?

148
00:08:16,079 --> 00:08:16,920
Blame me,

149
00:08:17,040 --> 00:08:18,440
I was just born with charming eyes.

150
00:08:18,959 --> 00:08:20,239
Charming eyes?

151
00:08:20,519 --> 00:08:21,399
Then, Young Master Lu Jiu,

152
00:08:21,440 --> 00:08:22,720
you must have a lot of admirers.

153
00:08:22,839 --> 00:08:23,720
That's not true.

154
00:08:23,799 --> 00:08:25,239
Out of all the rivers in the world,

155
00:08:25,359 --> 00:08:26,359
I only take one ladle.

156
00:08:26,359 --> 00:08:27,480
Among thousands of osmanthus blossoms,

157
00:08:27,600 --> 00:08:28,839
I only like you.

158
00:08:29,160 --> 00:08:30,119
Please, you two.

159
00:08:30,239 --> 00:08:31,440
Even if you don't care about me,

160
00:08:32,159 --> 00:08:33,840
at least consider that person's feelings.

161
00:08:40,239 --> 00:08:41,559
Ever since Lord Geng left,

162
00:08:41,679 --> 00:08:43,200
you've been downcast.

163
00:08:43,440 --> 00:08:45,039
You don't eat properly.

164
00:08:45,400 --> 00:08:46,400
Now, even when you walk,

165
00:08:46,520 --> 00:08:47,960
there's no strength in your steps.

166
00:08:48,119 --> 00:08:49,559
It's really worrying.

167
00:08:49,599 --> 00:08:51,239
Are you afraid I'll drag you all down?

168
00:08:51,479 --> 00:08:52,840
That's not what I mean.

169
00:08:52,880 --> 00:08:54,239
That is what you mean.

170
00:08:54,679 --> 00:08:56,159
You all dislike me.

171
00:08:56,559 --> 00:08:57,760
None of you want me anymore.

172
00:09:07,400 --> 00:09:09,039
Your feelings for Lord Geng

173
00:09:09,119 --> 00:09:10,719
are clear to all of us.

174
00:09:11,080 --> 00:09:13,599
Lord Geng is not a cold or unfeeling person.

175
00:09:13,719 --> 00:09:14,719
He acted this way

176
00:09:15,080 --> 00:09:17,000
because he must have his own reasons.

177
00:09:18,119 --> 00:09:19,239
What reasons could he have?

178
00:09:21,479 --> 00:09:23,520
Lord Geng is known for his integrity.

179
00:09:23,760 --> 00:09:25,960
He must have made many enemies at court.

180
00:09:26,000 --> 00:09:27,039
This time, as he returns,

181
00:09:27,119 --> 00:09:28,719
he must be facing some difficult problems.

182
00:09:28,799 --> 00:09:29,799
Leaving you here

183
00:09:30,000 --> 00:09:31,359
is to

184
00:09:31,799 --> 00:09:32,679
protect you.

185
00:09:33,280 --> 00:09:34,559
Protect me?

186
00:09:35,200 --> 00:09:36,440
He wants me to bring along

187
00:09:36,640 --> 00:09:38,200
someone who can't fight,

188
00:09:38,640 --> 00:09:40,200
someone whose skills are completely gone,

189
00:09:40,359 --> 00:09:42,520
someone unreliable whose abilities come and go,

190
00:09:42,599 --> 00:09:44,000
and venture deep into the dangerous Lone Mountain?

191
00:09:44,159 --> 00:09:45,520
You call that protecting me?

192
00:09:46,599 --> 00:09:47,840
Even though I've lost all my martial arts skills,

193
00:09:47,919 --> 00:09:49,000
I still have my wits.

194
00:09:49,039 --> 00:09:50,359
One person can be worth a thousand soldiers.

195
00:09:50,719 --> 00:09:52,640
Who are you calling useless?

196
00:09:52,799 --> 00:09:54,760
Even if my skills come and go,

197
00:09:54,799 --> 00:09:56,359
when have I ever

198
00:09:56,479 --> 00:09:57,239
let you down at a critical moment?

199
00:09:58,000 --> 00:09:58,919
Make yourself clear.

200
00:09:58,960 --> 00:09:59,960
Say it clearly.

201
00:10:01,640 --> 00:10:03,400
Spending all day with those two

202
00:10:03,479 --> 00:10:04,760
must be hard for you.

203
00:10:05,320 --> 00:10:07,119
Sorry to make Miss Bai Yu laugh.

204
00:10:14,479 --> 00:10:15,400
We've arrived at Lone Mountain.

205
00:10:19,080 --> 00:10:19,719
I...

206
00:10:19,799 --> 00:10:21,239
I think I've been here before.

207
00:10:32,919 --> 00:10:35,080
The imperial decree has arrived.

208
00:10:42,440 --> 00:10:45,320
By the Mandate of Heaven, the Emperor decrees:

209
00:10:45,440 --> 00:10:47,159
Geng Zhao of the Investigation Bureau,

210
00:10:47,239 --> 00:10:48,719
Diligent and hardworking,

211
00:10:48,840 --> 00:10:50,239
often solving difficult cases,

212
00:10:50,280 --> 00:10:51,760
greatly pleasing me.

213
00:10:51,919 --> 00:10:53,760
I hereby bestow three hundred taels of silver,

214
00:10:53,880 --> 00:10:55,599
and fifty bolts of silk,

215
00:10:55,679 --> 00:10:56,960
to make clear rewards and punishments,

216
00:10:57,000 --> 00:10:58,239
and to honor loyalty and virtue.

217
00:10:58,359 --> 00:11:00,039
This is my decree.

218
00:11:00,599 --> 00:11:01,840
Your subject Geng Zhao receives the decree.

219
00:11:04,280 --> 00:11:05,039
Lord Geng,

220
00:11:05,119 --> 00:11:06,359
please rise quickly.

221
00:11:08,239 --> 00:11:10,080
I also bring the Emperor's verbal message.

222
00:11:15,119 --> 00:11:16,320
Congratulations, Lord Geng.

223
00:11:16,320 --> 00:11:17,640
If this important matter succeeds,

224
00:11:17,679 --> 00:11:20,200
the Emperor will surely grant you marriage to Princess Bai Yu.

225
00:11:20,239 --> 00:11:21,799
Double happiness awaits you.

226
00:11:27,080 --> 00:11:29,559
I did not know Father had hidden Fei Ying's whereabouts for years

227
00:11:29,599 --> 00:11:30,679
to plan for a greater purpose.

228
00:11:31,599 --> 00:11:32,919
I nearly

229
00:11:33,599 --> 00:11:34,640
killed Fei Ying,

230
00:11:34,760 --> 00:11:36,280
and delayed Father's important plans.

231
00:11:36,440 --> 00:11:37,640
I ask Father to punish me.

232
00:11:43,159 --> 00:11:45,200
You are my only daughter.

233
00:11:45,440 --> 00:11:47,679
How could I ever punish you?

234
00:11:48,880 --> 00:11:51,799
Back then, I arranged your engagement with Fei Ying

235
00:11:51,880 --> 00:11:53,679
indeed to use it as a means

236
00:11:53,799 --> 00:11:56,000
Tie Fei Ying to Tianluo.

237
00:11:56,440 --> 00:11:58,640
But what father in this world

238
00:11:59,080 --> 00:12:02,000
would easily marry off his daughter to someone else?

239
00:12:02,080 --> 00:12:04,479
Fei Ying is the one I have chosen.

240
00:12:04,679 --> 00:12:06,520
He is also the one you have chosen.

241
00:12:07,239 --> 00:12:08,719
Since you want him,

242
00:12:08,919 --> 00:12:10,599
then take him back.

243
00:12:10,719 --> 00:12:14,119
That is the way our Dugu family does things.

244
00:12:14,479 --> 00:12:16,640
But how can a daughter take him back?

245
00:12:18,919 --> 00:12:22,200
Do you know how I made Tianluo

246
00:12:22,280 --> 00:12:24,719
grow from an obscure assassination organization

247
00:12:24,760 --> 00:12:28,000
into one that holds power over the entire court?

248
00:12:29,520 --> 00:12:31,239
Of course, it was because of my outstanding abilities.

249
00:12:31,359 --> 00:12:32,599
I was able to ease the emperor's worries.

250
00:12:32,880 --> 00:12:34,280
Especially twenty years ago,

251
00:12:34,440 --> 00:12:36,679
when I personally wiped out the traitors of Fengleitang.

252
00:12:36,919 --> 00:12:37,960
I earned the emperor's deep trust.

253
00:12:38,039 --> 00:12:41,520
There are countless people trusted by the emperor.

254
00:12:41,559 --> 00:12:43,719
What sets me apart from them is

255
00:12:44,479 --> 00:12:47,799
that I alone hold the emperor's troubles in my hands.

256
00:12:51,599 --> 00:12:54,840
Fengleitang never actually rebelled.

257
00:12:55,880 --> 00:12:59,039
But if I say they rebelled, then they did.

258
00:12:59,719 --> 00:13:01,640
If I want their whole clan destroyed,

259
00:13:01,679 --> 00:13:03,359
then they must be destroyed.

260
00:13:04,440 --> 00:13:08,400
They became the stepping stone for my rise to power.

261
00:13:12,320 --> 00:13:13,840
Father, you mean

262
00:13:15,280 --> 00:13:16,559
planning depends on people,

263
00:13:17,599 --> 00:13:19,080
and so does success.

264
00:13:20,159 --> 00:13:21,159
Yes.

265
00:13:29,919 --> 00:13:31,039
That's right.

266
00:13:35,239 --> 00:13:37,840
Wipe out the remaining rebels of Gushan immediately.

267
00:13:41,919 --> 00:13:44,320
The court has tolerated the Gushan group for many years.

268
00:13:44,679 --> 00:13:46,799
Why suddenly order their extermination now?

269
00:13:53,119 --> 00:13:54,080
Who is it?

270
00:15:00,119 --> 00:15:01,119
Don't pretend with me.

271
00:15:01,320 --> 00:15:02,000
Stop pretending.

272
00:15:02,080 --> 00:15:03,239
Waiter, the bill.

273
00:15:03,679 --> 00:15:04,479
Coming.

274
00:15:04,880 --> 00:15:05,919
Brother, no, no, no.

275
00:15:06,000 --> 00:15:07,280
I'll pay today.

276
00:15:07,320 --> 00:15:08,080
Don't move.

277
00:15:08,840 --> 00:15:10,599
I didn't expect them to look so fierce.

278
00:15:10,679 --> 00:15:11,599
But they're actually quite friendly.

279
00:15:17,280 --> 00:15:18,479
Come, let's see the doctor.

280
00:15:19,520 --> 00:15:20,080
Let's go.

