562
00:28:18,079 --> 00:28:19,640
she's not such a cold person.

563
00:28:24,599 --> 00:28:25,839
No need to guess anymore.

564
00:28:26,119 --> 00:28:27,520
So she's not mute after all.

565
00:28:28,880 --> 00:28:30,439
Back then, you told me to run away.

566
00:28:30,599 --> 00:28:32,359
But wherever I go, it's still the jianghu.

567
00:28:32,560 --> 00:28:35,160
Only by following the strongest can one survive in the jianghu.

568
00:28:57,079 --> 00:28:58,760
Madam, I've brought the person.

569
00:29:05,199 --> 00:29:06,800
So you are the Laundry Woman.

570
00:29:07,079 --> 00:29:09,040
You're not some old crone at all.

571
00:29:09,760 --> 00:29:11,680
It's fortunate he didn't see you.

572
00:29:13,520 --> 00:29:15,040
I've long heard of the Laundry Woman's reputation.

573
00:29:15,119 --> 00:29:17,040
To meet you today is truly a blessing.

574
00:29:17,439 --> 00:29:18,560
You've committed many wrongs.

575
00:29:18,719 --> 00:29:20,319
Today, we're here to uphold justice.

576
00:29:20,880 --> 00:29:21,880
Let's do it.

577
00:29:23,680 --> 00:29:25,560
You're the first person after meeting me

578
00:29:25,640 --> 00:29:27,400
who can still stand so firm.

579
00:29:27,479 --> 00:29:28,439
But

580
00:29:28,760 --> 00:29:31,160
Underestimating your opponent is a grave mistake in our world.

581
00:29:36,439 --> 00:29:37,239
What,

582
00:29:37,439 --> 00:29:38,439
young man,

583
00:29:38,599 --> 00:29:39,680
are you giving up already?

584
00:29:39,760 --> 00:29:40,479
I, Lu Jiu,

585
00:29:40,599 --> 00:29:41,839
have never admitted defeat.

586
00:29:44,640 --> 00:29:45,640
Lu Jiu.

587
00:29:46,839 --> 00:29:48,640
Lu Jiu of the Lu family in Luoyang County.

588
00:29:50,160 --> 00:29:51,640
I never change my name or hide my identity.

589
00:29:57,959 --> 00:29:58,959
What are you doing?

590
00:30:03,119 --> 00:30:04,160
My son!

591
00:30:04,599 --> 00:30:07,040
Mother has finally found you.

592
00:30:49,479 --> 00:30:51,839
Lu Jiu has never liked interacting with people.

593
00:30:52,680 --> 00:30:55,160
I still remember the first time I met him.

594
00:30:55,479 --> 00:30:56,599
I almost fell down.

595
00:30:56,640 --> 00:30:58,079
He didn't even help me up.

596
00:30:58,959 --> 00:31:00,520
It made me embarrass myself in front of everyone.

597
00:31:03,599 --> 00:31:04,640
According to what you said,

598
00:31:04,839 --> 00:31:06,119
the actions of that Taoist

599
00:31:06,199 --> 00:31:07,560
were all done behind Gushan's back.

600
00:31:07,719 --> 00:31:08,520
That's right.

601
00:31:08,920 --> 00:31:10,640
Madam has always managed things well.

602
00:31:10,839 --> 00:31:12,959
Although Gushan shelters people from the underworld,

603
00:31:13,040 --> 00:31:14,680
each one of them is a person of justice.

604
00:31:14,880 --> 00:31:15,959
She would never allow her subordinates

605
00:31:16,000 --> 00:31:17,319
to get involved in human trafficking.

606
00:31:17,439 --> 00:31:18,719
Then what about the Heroes' Gathering just now?

607
00:31:18,800 --> 00:31:20,079
How do you explain that?

608
00:31:21,760 --> 00:31:23,359
Those who were bought and sold

609
00:31:23,520 --> 00:31:25,199
are all people guilty of heinous crimes.

610
00:31:25,760 --> 00:31:27,000
After I subdued them,

611
00:31:27,079 --> 00:31:28,560
I didn't want to take their lives.

612
00:31:28,760 --> 00:31:29,719
This Heroes' Society

613
00:31:29,800 --> 00:31:32,079
is meant to give them a chance to reform.

614
00:31:32,280 --> 00:31:33,920
After they are sold to buyers,

615
00:31:34,000 --> 00:31:36,560
all uses will be supervised by us

616
00:31:36,760 --> 00:31:39,040
to ensure they won't harm the martial world again.

617
00:31:39,400 --> 00:31:41,719
Creating drugged people is what you call "battle maniacs."

618
00:31:41,839 --> 00:31:43,239
For the safety of the martial world,

619
00:31:43,479 --> 00:31:44,880
that person brought it upon himself.

620
00:31:45,280 --> 00:31:47,079
He colluded with that old Taoist.

621
00:31:47,119 --> 00:31:48,839
They stole the secret recipe for making drugged people.

622
00:31:48,880 --> 00:31:51,079
They secretly turned living people into drugged people and sold them.

623
00:31:51,280 --> 00:31:52,839
The old woman was just using their own methods

624
00:31:52,880 --> 00:31:54,439
to deal with them.

625
00:31:54,599 --> 00:31:56,160
I am from the Hall of Wind and Thunder.

626
00:31:56,280 --> 00:31:58,280
The hall master, Luo Feng, is highly skilled in medicine.

627
00:31:58,760 --> 00:32:00,400
After discovering the method for making drugged people,

628
00:32:00,560 --> 00:32:02,199
fearing it would harm the martial world,

629
00:32:02,400 --> 00:32:03,880
he sealed the method away.

630
00:32:03,920 --> 00:32:05,160
I respect the hall master

631
00:32:05,280 --> 00:32:07,040
and would never disobey his orders.

632
00:32:07,439 --> 00:32:08,880
No wonder those criminals used

633
00:32:08,920 --> 00:32:10,760
Blood Scorpion, Tianxiong, Amethyst,

634
00:32:10,839 --> 00:32:12,400
Qianhu, Bajiji, Southern Star

635
00:32:12,439 --> 00:32:13,959
as secret codes for entering and exiting.

636
00:32:14,079 --> 00:32:15,640
They're all names of medicinal herbs.

637
00:32:16,400 --> 00:32:17,520
And that old Taoist

638
00:32:17,640 --> 00:32:19,079
is truly despicable.

639
00:32:19,400 --> 00:32:20,359
Just like Li Mu,

640
00:32:20,439 --> 00:32:21,599
he actually used medicine to harm people.

641
00:32:21,760 --> 00:32:22,959
We caused a commotion at the Heroes' Society earlier.

642
00:32:23,239 --> 00:32:24,599
That was our mistake.

643
00:32:37,560 --> 00:32:39,359
There is still one thing I don't understand.

644
00:32:40,199 --> 00:32:42,239
Why are you able to take charge of Gushan,

645
00:32:42,719 --> 00:32:44,439
but abandoned Lu Jiu back then?

646
00:32:47,280 --> 00:32:49,359
It's not that I didn't want to look for him.

647
00:32:50,800 --> 00:32:52,599
But that treacherous Li Chu

648
00:32:52,599 --> 00:32:54,119
hid Jiu'er away.

649
00:32:54,439 --> 00:32:56,000
I searched everywhere, north and south of the great river,

650
00:32:56,079 --> 00:32:57,640
but found no news of him.

651
00:33:00,760 --> 00:33:01,640
Li Chu.

652
00:33:02,239 --> 00:33:03,239
I know about this.

653
00:33:03,680 --> 00:33:06,280
Li Chu was the second-in-command of Fenglei Hall back then.

654
00:33:07,239 --> 00:33:09,040
Fenglei Hall rebelled that year.

655
00:33:09,239 --> 00:33:10,599
Dugu was ordered to suppress the rebellion.

656
00:33:10,920 --> 00:33:12,439
He was the one who coordinated from inside and out.

657
00:33:12,800 --> 00:33:13,800
But afterwards,

658
00:33:13,880 --> 00:33:15,479
he disappeared without a trace.

659
00:33:16,040 --> 00:33:17,680
Fenglei Hall never rebelled.

660
00:33:17,839 --> 00:33:20,040
It was Li Chu and Dugu Wuwo who colluded.

661
00:33:20,439 --> 00:33:22,680
They falsely claimed that Master Luo possessed the Wuxiang treasure.

662
00:33:22,760 --> 00:33:24,400
and would threaten the court and the nation.

663
00:33:24,959 --> 00:33:25,920
In fact,

664
00:33:26,400 --> 00:33:29,079
they were the ones who wanted to seize the treasure.
